text.tspan: Ankur Panwar, Bhavesh Jadav, Mentor: Parin Chheda, Saurav Shandilya, Vishwanathan

flowRoot.flowPara: INTRODUCTION: This project logs crop data in a green house to reduce manual labour.
Essentialy, it is a weighing machine connected to internet.

A weighing machine will measure weight, take input from user related to crop and take image of crop. After successful data entry, data will automatically pushed to database. Local people can also take advantage of crop production by placing order through e-commerce website.
We can use image processing for crop details.We can replace keypad and LCD by touch pad.
The model can be transformed into more compact version.
